{"tid":1822620,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【想贏嘅同我入嚟】一人一信逼英國做嘢","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T05:29:53.000Z","uid":282535,"like":53,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"1e93cacd32d0eb84df6953150b4187d8553d8e72","tid":1822620,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/807mptt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F807mptt.jpg&h=42a58fea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0G1m8Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0G1m8Va.jpg&h=4c779cde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvY1ptw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvY1ptw.jpg&h=dd01a795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#一人一信 #鍵盤戰士<br />\n❗️英國戰線要人❗️<br />\n🔥鍵盤戰士到你地出手🔥<br />\n<br />\n我地琴晚已經出左一篇<span style=\"color: red;\">formal email比英國首相，外交部同上下議院議員。促請英國</span> :<br />\n<br />\n1)回應<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警於英領執法嫌疑違反《維也納領事關係公約》</span></span><br />\n2)<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為英領被捕手足提供協助</span></span><br />\n3)回應留守者訴求 : 終止《中英聯合聲明》，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重啟三條條約收回香港，並協助香港獨立，以解決2047大限問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日黑警可以任意濫捕，正正因為港共賦予黑警無限大嘅權力。所以<span style=\"color: red;\">我地必須奪回主權，只有主權在民，先有真正民主。</span><br />\n<br />\n⚠️大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\">copy我地篇email(鍾意可以加埋相)，一人一信炸爆佢地信箱求救</span>📪⚠️<br />\ntemplate: <a href=\"http://t.me/ukterminatejd/346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukterminatejd%2F346&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=78818ba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ukterminatejd/346</a><br />\n相: <a href=\"http://t.me/ukterminatejd/347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukterminatejd%2F347&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=f7d9a4b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ukterminatejd/347</a><br />\n<br />\nEmail list:<br />\nboris.johnson.mp@parliament.uk,<br />\ndominic.raab.mp@parliament.uk,<br />\nalistair.carmichael@parliament.uk,<br />\nchris.whitehouse@whitehouseconsulting.co.uk,<br />\ncontactholmember@parliament.uk,<br />\nhcenquiries@parliament.uk<br />\n<br />\n香港人，我地親自，<br />\n為自己、為手足發聲🔥<br />\n<br />\n#香港獨立 #唯一出路<br />\n#終止聲明 #重啟三條條約<br />\n#脫共解殖 #重奪主權 #回歸英聯邦<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n英國戰線tg channel <a href=\"http://t.me/ukterminatejd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukterminatejd&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a9f01ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ukterminatejd</a>"},{"pid":"c7738d9efaebff686ab4a558882e6d56bacf4425","tid":1822620,"uid":282535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">複製下文狂寄去英國Template for Reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\nEmail <br />\n<br />\nSubject: Urgent Request for Solving Humanity Crisis in Hong Kong, including at the British Embassy in Admiralty<br />\n<br />\nDear&nbsp;Prime Minister, FCO, Members of the&nbsp;All-Party Parliamentary Group on Hong Kong,&nbsp;Members of the House of Lords, and Members of the House of Commons,<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nI am writing to ask Britain to<br />\n1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;immediately respond to the violation of the Vienna Convention on Consular Relations by the Hong Kong Riot Police who repeatedly enforced HKSAR law on the British territory and threatened the personal safety of people within,&nbsp;<br />\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;provide all necessary assistance to the protestor kidnapped by the Riot Police at the British Embassy in Hong Kong, and&nbsp;<br />\n3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;take actions on China for its breach of the Sino-British Joint Declaration (JD). Considering the One Country, Two System has completely failed, we request Britain to help us leave China completely and achieve independence.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nIncident on 11-12 January 2020<br />\nIn the afternoon on 11 January 2020, peaceful protestors, including those camping at the British Embassy in Hong Kong for personal safety and asking for the termination of the JD, were harassed by the Riot Police. They were threatened by the riots using pepper spray and had their HKID copied for potential compilation of social credit system. One underaged protestors were kidnapped within the territory of the British Embassy. At the scene, protestors banged the window at the British Embassy in hope the staff inside would at least provide assistance, but the staff there refused to respond at all."},{"pid":"4650816d8859d0c63370c82d248a54f0d678003b","tid":1822620,"uid":282535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"Netizens therefore initiated visiting the British Embassy peacefully in the evening on 12 January 2020, hoping to ask Britain to condemn Hong Kong Riot Police for violating the Vienna Convention or explain involvement of the British Embassy in the incident, give a formal reply for the negligence of the security guard, and to help the arrested protestor. However, around 30 Riot Police stationed outside the British Embassy since early morning trying to intimidate both visitors to the British Embassy and protestors camping there. In the evening, around 300 police occupied the whole Admiralty, and performed stop-and-search on passerby, visitors, first-aiders and journalists within the area of the British Embassy.&nbsp;Journalists were chased away from the area, and more Hongkongers were kidnapped near the Embassy. When the protestor standing within the area of the British Embassy were being interviewed by journalists, a group of Riot Police circled around to intimidate her.<br />\n<br />\nFailure of One Country, Two System&nbsp;<br />\nThere is no more freedom and safety for Hong Kong people, because the rule of law and the separation of power have been completely sabotaged. The One Country, Two System is still &ldquo;enforced&rdquo; now but has completely failed, making it unrealistic to try to &ldquo;uphold&rdquo; it. We, therefore, request Britain to terminate the JD which has been repeatedly violated by China, and help Hong Kong achieve independence, so that we can have a democratic government which positively responds citizens&rsquo; demands, and achieve prosperity in Hong Kong again.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nCall for Action&nbsp;<br />\nThis is the challenge of our times, for both Britain and Hong Kong, once again after 35 years. Britain must stop showing sign of weakness,&nbsp;and grab the chance to make a substantial difference for the future of Hong Kong sovereignty.&nbsp;We hereby request the British Government to take actions on the situation of the&nbsp;kidnapped protestor, and help solve the humanity crisis in Hong Kong by terminating China&rsquo;s sovereignty over Hong Kong.&nbsp; Help Hong Kong become an independent Nation like all other former British colonies.<br />\n<br />\nWe look forward to a positive response by the British Government. For official reply, you may send to ukterminatejd@gmail.com . Thank you.<br />\n<br />\nRegards<br />\n(你個筆名)<br />\nHongkonger"},{"pid":"029b780f6e3de2a0ef026a8e419b7db3e7b03350","tid":1822620,"uid":32180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:25:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a02ff874ae62210502334ec59f97b35585a4191","tid":1822620,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=e8aa51e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter要人】國際人權監察阿頭被港府無理拒絕入境，外媒大肆報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"221646cb4b0a4ab9e4a1876f79c4b76e5b593ba6","tid":1822620,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"a2ef25c907a90e438b06c4b7c659afc1ccdbff46","tid":1822620,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45bd1c88c47ab61d8c3b9ed4966b4dbccc6771e","tid":1822620,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"點解會冇人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dccca627ffe56507fab057252dedab65dd47b1","tid":1822620,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"係咪咁多人都咁想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇人推<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"688393fa7d455a22b6d19a492377baad4bc7e5de","tid":1822620,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4c1164ae468a4d1aa07209909b40c45875d9992","tid":1822620,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"Done !<br />\nSend左"},{"pid":"9d920e15c904ec3d2ac1062b0fa534d63cb368dc","